channel.title: Some people cannot load
channel.description:
I've made a webclient which runs fine for me and some others, but some people get a white screen and a little red cross saying "error, click for details." after some searching and experimenting i found that you need JDK to run my webclient. which i figured is why nobody wants or can play my server.
could anybody help me? i will rep++ for any help
